## 1) Summary

The platform combines AI-guided scheduling, day-of travel support, waiting-room intake, provider summary generation, post-visit surveys, and future follow-up reminders to improve access, efficiency, and continuity of care.

---

## 2) End-to-End Workflow

### Patient Journey (Tree)

```text
Patient Care Workflow
├── 1. Patient opens portal and enters symptom/concern
├── 2. AI suggests providers and appointment slots
├── 3. Patient schedules or reschedules
├── 4. AI confirms appointment and sets reminders/calendar hooks
├── 5. Day-of AI checks traffic and suggests departure time
├── 6. Patient arrives and checks in
├── 7. AI waiting-room assistant collects updates/questions
├── 8. AI generates provider summary
├── 9. Provider reviews summary and conducts focused visit
└── 10. Post-visit engagement and continuity
    ├── 10.1 Visit completion event is received
    ├── 10.2 Patient receives post-visit reminder
    ├── 10.3 Patient receives quick experience survey
    ├── 10.4 Follow-up plan starts (typically 6-12 months)
    ├── 10.5 System monitors provider schedule availability
    ├── 10.6 Alert sent when relevant future slots open
    └── 10.7 Patient books next visit directly in portal
```

